General.Name: Visiber57 Corp
General.Description: Visiber57 Corp. focuses on acquiring, developing, and launching a cloud-based application that utilizes a predictive algorithm to foster closely knitted communities made up of individuals, families, and businesses from various background. The company was formerly known as eBizware, Inc. and changed its name to Visiber57 Corp. in April 2017. Visiber57 Corp. was incorporated in 2013 and is headquartered in Taipei, Taiwan. Visiber57 Corp. is a subsidiary of 57 Society International Limited.
